# Project Specification

The authoritative specification lives in `docs/gnucash_email_receipt_categorization_spec.mdc`.
Always consult that file for domain rules, acceptance criteria, and input/output contracts.

Key quick-reference points (see spec file for full details):

- Target accounts: `Unspecified`, `Imbalance-GBP` only
- GBP only; skip mixed-currency and future-dated transactions
- User approval is mandatory before any write
- Not all transactions have emails; not all emails have transactions; receipts often absent
- New categories allowed; evidence approval drives enrichment
